---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const ayanBreadcrumbData = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "首页", "item": "https://amz.hao1234.top/" },
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "公开课", "item": "https://amz.hao1234.top/open-class/" },
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "新品 PPC 首周广告结构课", "item": "https://amz.hao1234.top/open-class/ppc-week-one/" }
  ]
};
---
<BaseLayout
  title="新品 PPC 首周广告结构课 · 公开课详情"
  description="新品上架第一周广告怎么开、预算怎么分、数据怎么看，帮新手建立低风险的新品首周 PPC 测试节奏。"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(ayanBreadcrumbData)}></script>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow">第 2 节 · 新品 PPC</div>
      <h1>新品 PPC 首周广告结构课</h1>
      <p>帮新手建立低风险的新品首周 PPC 测试节奏。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="info-grid">
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-label">适合谁</div>
        <div class="info-value">新品刚上线、不知道自动广告和手动广告怎么分工、不知道首周广告该看哪些指标的卖家</div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-label">解决什么问题</div>
        <div class="info-value">帮新手建立低风险的新品首周 PPC 测试节奏</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="detail-block">
      <h2>课程结构</h2>
      <ol class="step-list">
        <li>
          <div class="step-num">1</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <div class="step-title">新品首周广告目标</div>
            <div class="step-desc">第一周广告不是为了赚钱，是为了跑数据。曝光、点击、搜索词收录——这三个指标比 ACOS 更值得关注。</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="step-num">2</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <div class="step-title">自动广告怎么开</div>
            <div class="step-desc">自动广告的作用是探测系统对产品的理解。四种匹配方式的预算分配和出价策略，首周自动广告的预期数据范围。</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="step-num">3</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <div class="step-title">手动精准词怎么放</div>
            <div class="step-desc">从关键词表里选出 5-10 个核心精准词开手动，出价策略、匹配方式、预算占比。手动不是越广越好。</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="step-num">4</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <div class="step-title">搜索词报告怎么看</div>
            <div class="step-desc">首周搜索词报告的核心字段：曝光词、点击词、转化词分别怎么判断。哪些词应该保留、哪些词应该否定。</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="step-num">5</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <div class="step-title">什么时候否词</div>
            <div class="step-desc">新品第一周否词的节奏：太早否词会屏蔽数据，太晚否词会烧预算。首周否词的判断标准。</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="step-num">6</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <div class="step-title">首周复盘表怎么填</div>
            <div class="step-desc">用 PPC 周复盘表记录首周数据：预算消耗、曝光量、点击率、CPC、搜索词收录数。第 7 天的数据决定第 8 天的调整方向。</div>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="detail-block">
      <h2>对应文章</h2>
      <div class="related-grid">
        <a class="related-card" href="/articles/ppc-learning-path/">
          <div class="related-tag">学习路径</div>
          <h3>亚马逊 PPC 广告学习路径</h3>
          <p>从结构搭建到数据判断的完整路线，本节课程的体系框架。</p>
        </a>
        <a class="related-card" href="/articles/new-product-ppc-week-one/">
          <div class="related-tag">实操文章</div>
          <h3>新品广告第一周怎么开</h3>
          <p>预算、关键词和否词策略，首周广告的完整执行指南。</p>
        </a>
        <a class="related-card" href="/articles/sp-ad-structure/">
          <div class="related-tag">实操文章</div>
          <h3>SP 广告结构</h3>
          <p>自动、精准、词组、竞品四类广告的分工和预算分配。</p>
        </a>
        <a class="related-card" href="/articles/ai-ppc-report-review/">
          <div class="related-tag">实操文章</div>
          <h3>如何用 AI 复盘广告报表</h3>
          <p>用 AI 辅助判断搜索词报告和广告数据，提升复盘效率。</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="detail-block">
      <h2>对应资料包</h2>
      <a class="learning-path-card" href="/resources/ppc-weekly-review/">
        <div class="lp-hint">配套资料</div>
        <h3>PPC 周复盘表</h3>
        <p>首周广告数据记录和复盘模板，带学员跑通 7 天预算分配和调整节奏。</p>
        <span class="lp-cta">查看资料详情 →</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="detail-block">
      <h2>微信关键词</h2>
      <div class="wechat-block">
        <span class="wechat-badge">报表</span>
        <p>回复关键词"报表"，领取配套资料包。</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-block">
      <h2>准备开始实操</h2>
      <p>建议先阅读对应文章，再配合资料包做课后演练。</p>
      <div class="cta-actions">
        <a class="cta-primary" href="/resources/ppc-weekly-review/">查看 PPC 周复盘表</a>
        <a class="cta-secondary" href="/open-class/">回到公开课中心</a>
        <a class="cta-secondary" href="/resources/">回到资源中心</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="callout-amber">
      <strong>⚠ 使用边界</strong>
      <p>不承诺降低 ACOS 或保证出单。广告判断要结合预算、类目竞争和转化数据。不同类目的首周广告数据差异很大，复盘表的填法需要根据实际类目调整。</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 18% 28%, rgba(19, 104, 255, 0.10), transparent 26%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #f5f8fd 0%, #eef3fa 100%);
    padding: 56px 24px 48px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.8);
  }

  .page-hero-inner {
    max-width: 1180px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #eaf2ff;
    color: #1368ff;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.4px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    border: 1px solid #cfe0ff;
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    font-size: 42px;
    line-height: 1.18;
    letter-spacing: -1.4px;
    color: #0f172a;
  }

  .page-hero p {
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 760px;
    color: #475569;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .section {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 34px 24px;
  }

  .info-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
    margin: 0 0 32px;
  }

  .info-card {
    padding: 18px 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fffcf0 0%, #fef6e0 100%);
    border: 1px solid #f4d089;
    border-radius: 14px;
  }

  .info-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #b45309;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.4px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .info-value {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #1f2937;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .detail-block {
    margin: 0 0 36px;
  }

  .detail-block h2 {
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: #0f172a;
    letter-spacing: -0.3px;
  }

  .detail-block p {
    color: #475569;
    line-height: 1.85;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .step-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .step-list li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 16px 18px;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 14px;
  }

  .step-num {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1368ff, #3b82f6);
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .step-body {
    flex: 1 1 auto;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .step-title {
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #0f172a;
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .step-desc {
    color: #475569;
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .related-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .related-card {
    display: block;
    padding: 18px 20px;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 14px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease;
  }

  .related-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: #cfe0ff;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(19, 104, 255, 0.08);
  }

  .related-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    padding: 3px 9px;
    background: #eef5ff;
    color: #1368ff;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 900;
    border-radius: 999px;
  }

  .related-card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #0f172a;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .related-card p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #475569;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .learning-path-card {
    display: block;
    padding: 22px 26px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eef5ff 0%, #f0f7ff 100%);
    border: 1px solid #cfe0ff;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .learning-path-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: #93c5fd;
    box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(19, 104, 255, 0.14);
  }

  .lp-hint {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #1368ff;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.4px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .learning-path-card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    color: #0f172a;
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  .learning-path-card p {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    color: #475569;
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .lp-cta {
    color: #1368ff;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .wechat-block {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #ecfdf5 100%);
    border: 1px solid #a7f3d0;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .wechat-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    height: 32px;
    padding: 0 14px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #059669;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 13px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .wechat-block p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #065f46;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .cta-block {
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    padding: 28px 32px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fffcf0 0%, #fef6e0 100%);
    border: 1px solid #f4d089;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-block h2 {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    color: #0f172a;
    font-size: 24px;
    letter-spacing: -0.4px;
  }

  .cta-block p {
    margin: 0 0 22px;
    color: #475569;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .cta-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cta-primary,
  .cta-secondary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 46px;
    padding: 0 24px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 14px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .cta-primary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1368ff, #3b82f6);
    color: #ffffff;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(19, 104, 255, 0.22);
  }

  .cta-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(19, 104, 255, 0.32);
  }

  .cta-secondary {
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #1368ff;
    border: 1px solid #cfe0ff;
  }

  .cta-secondary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: #93c5fd;
  }

  .callout-amber {
    padding: 20px 24px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fffcf0 0%, #fef6e0 100%);
    border: 1px solid #f4d089;
    border-left: 4px solid #d97706;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .callout-amber strong {
    display: block;
    color: #b45309;
    font-size: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .callout-amber p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #57534e;
    line-height: 1.85;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .page-hero h1 {
      font-size: 30px;
    }
    .info-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .related-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
